org.kepler.objectmanager.library

Class LibItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kepler.objectmanager.library.LibItem

  • public class LibItem
extends java.lang.Object
    The LibItem class represents one node of the Component Library Tree. The data in this class corresponds directly to the columns of the Library_Index table as well as the data stored in auxiliary tables through foreign key references.
    Author:
    Aaron Schultz

        public void delete(java.sql.Statement stmt)
